    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine Domini nostri Iehsu Christi Dei eterni, anno ab incarnatione
                        (…) (mil)lesimo centesimo sexagesimo tertio, septimo kal. maii, indictione
                        undecima. Manifesti sumus nos <persName><name ref="Strambus"
                            >Strambus</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Heinricus"
                                >Henricus</name></persName> atque <persName><name ref="Villanus"
                                >Villanus</name></persName> germani quondam filii <persName><name
                                ref="Aldebertus Manciolini">Aldibertini
                        Manciolini</name></persName>, et <persName><name ref="Emma"
                            >Emma</name></persName> uxor suprascripti Strambi et filia
                                <persName><name ref="Ildebrandinus">Ildebrandini</name></persName>
                        et <persName><name ref="Alamanna">Alamanna</name></persName> uxor
                        suprascripti Henrici et quondam filia <persName><name ref="Porcellus"
                                >Porcelli</name></persName> atque <persName><name ref="Gasdia"
                                >Gasdia</name></persName> uxor suprascripti Villani et quondam filia
                                <persName><name ref="Rodelosso">Rodelossi</name></persName>, (…) ubi
                        interfuit notitia <persName><name ref="Lotteringus"
                            >Lotteringhi</name></persName> iudicis domni imperatoris (…),
                            <foreign>che</foreign> per hanc cartulam vendimus et tra(dimus) (…)
                        gratia custodi et rectori <orgName key="#Hospitals"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3206"><rs key="#Hospitals">hospitalis</rs>
                            Sancti Gilii</orgName> de loco <placeName key="#Hospitals"
                            ref="#places/3207">Altepascio</placeName>, (…) unam videlicet petiam de
                        terra nostra que est campus et ortus et lama in (…) capanna veteri super se
                        cum tabulis et tino que esse videtur in loco ubi dicitur <placeName
                            ref="#places/3242">Graticciola</placeName>. Et tenet unum caput in terra
                        et media fossa <persName><name ref="Vitalis">Vitalis</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Petrus Rofredi">Petri
                            Roffredi</name></persName>, alterum caput in terra et media fossa
                                <persName><name ref="Bertram">Bertrahimi</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Gherardinus Malsegiori">Gerardini
                                Malsegiori</name></persName>, latus in terra et media fossa
                        suprascripti Bertrahimi et in terra et media fossa suprascripti Vitalis et
                        in terra et media fossa <persName><name ref="Richardus"
                            >Ricciardi</name></persName> testoris, aliud latus in via publica. (…)
                            <foreign>Dimensioni</foreign>: modiora sex et dimidium.
                            <foreign>Prezzo</foreign>: (sol.) nonaginta et quinque bonorum lucensium
                        denariorum. <foreign>Pena</foreign>: in duplum (…) insuper penam argenti
                        optimi libras quadraginta et sub pena etiam consulum (…) lucensium
                        presentium vel futurorum et luc. potestatis que pro tempore fuerit. (…)
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Bonannus">Bonianni</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Hubertellus de la Stramba">Ubertelli de la
                                Stramba</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Ildebrandus">Ildebrandi</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Villanus">Villani</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Bectus">Becchi</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Widuccius">Guiducii</name></persName> rogatorum
                            <rs key="#Witness">testium</rs>. <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name
                                ref="Dulcis">Dulcis</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> domni imperatoris (…).</ab>
                </div>
